/-! ## Vanishing of `bch_septic_term` on `(Œ±‚Ä¢V, Œ≤‚Ä¢V)`

Since `bch(Œ±‚Ä¢V, Œ≤‚Ä¢V) = log(exp(Œ±‚Ä¢V)¬∑exp(Œ≤‚Ä¢V)) = (Œ±+Œ≤)‚Ä¢V` for any
