-- The degree-4 pure identity: verified by noncomm_ring at Ring level (no ùïÇ needed).
-- After √ó24 clearing: the Y‚ÇÑ-¬Ω(Y‚ÇÅY‚ÇÉ+Y‚ÇÇ¬≤+Y‚ÇÉY‚ÇÅ)+‚Öì(Y‚ÇÅ¬≤Y‚ÇÇ+...)-¬ºY‚ÇÅ‚Å¥+C‚ÇÑ = 0.
