/-- **I‚ÇÇ residual decomposition**: pure ring identity in `(z, P, T‚ÇÇ, T‚ÇÉ)` for
`(z+P)¬≥ - z¬≥ - (z¬≤T‚ÇÇ+zT‚ÇÇz+T‚ÇÇz¬≤) - (z¬≤T‚ÇÉ+zT‚ÇÉz+T‚ÇÉz¬≤+zT‚ÇÇ¬≤+T‚ÇÇzT‚ÇÇ+T‚ÇÇ¬≤z)`,
which when multiplied by `(3:ùïÇ)‚Åª¬π` becomes `I‚ÇÇ - corr‚ÇÇ - corr‚ÇÇ_5`.

Each summand on the RHS has deg-6+ structure (since `P-T‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÉ` has deg-4+,
`P¬≤-T‚ÇÇ¬≤` has deg-5+, `PzP-T‚ÇÇzT‚ÇÇ` has deg-6+, `P¬≥` has deg-6). -/
private theorem I2_residual_decomp_eq (z P T‚ÇÇ T‚ÇÉ : ùî∏) :
    (z + P) ^ 3 - z ^ 3 -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÇ + z * T‚ÇÇ * z + T‚ÇÇ * z ^ 2) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÉ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 + T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ + T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 * z) =
    z ^ 2 * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ) + z * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ) * z + (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ) * z ^ 2 +
    z * (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2) + (P * z * P - T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ) +
    (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2) * z + P ^ 3 := by
  noncomm_ring

/-- **I‚ÇÇ septic residual decomposition**: extends `I2_residual_decomp_eq`
by subtracting the deg-6 leading part `y3_6 = (3 T‚ÇÑ terms) + (6 T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÉ
permutations) + T‚ÇÇ¬≥` to give a pure ring identity in `(z, P, T‚ÇÇ, T‚ÇÉ, T‚ÇÑ)`
where each RHS term is deg-7+.

Pairings:
- `(3 T‚ÇÑ terms)` extend the 3 weight-1 (P-T‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÉ) terms into (P-T‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÑ).
- `(6 T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÉ perms)` are absorbed into the 3 weight-2 (P¬≤-T‚ÇÇ¬≤) compound
  forms, giving `z(P¬≤-T‚ÇÇ¬≤-T‚ÇÇT‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÉT‚ÇÇ)`, `(PzP-T‚ÇÇzT‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÇzT‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÉzT‚ÇÇ)`,
  `(P¬≤-T‚ÇÇ¬≤-T‚ÇÇT‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÉT‚ÇÇ)z`.
- `T‚ÇÇ¬≥` is absorbed into `P¬≥`, giving `P¬≥ - T‚ÇÇ¬≥` (deg-7+ via telescoping).

Each summand on the RHS is deg-7+ in the BCH context.
Proof: `noncomm_ring` (pure ring identity, no scalar coefficients). -/
private theorem I2_septic_residual_decomp_eq (z P T‚ÇÇ T‚ÇÉ T‚ÇÑ : ùî∏) :
    (z + P) ^ 3 - z ^ 3 -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÇ + z * T‚ÇÇ * z + T‚ÇÇ * z ^ 2) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÉ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 + T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ + T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 * z) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÑ + z * T‚ÇÑ * z + T‚ÇÑ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÉ + T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ * z +
        T‚ÇÇ ^ 3) =
    z ^ 2 * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ) + z * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ) * z +
      (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ) * z ^ 2 +
    z * (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ) +
    (P * z * P - T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÇ) +
    (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ) * z +
    (P ^ 3 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 3) := by
  noncomm_ring

/-- **I‚ÇÇ octic residual decomposition**: extends `I2_septic_residual_decomp_eq`
by subtracting the deg-7 leading part `y3_7` (15 terms: 3 with T‚ÇÖ, 6 with
T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÑ + T‚ÇÑ¬∑T‚ÇÇ perms, 3 with T‚ÇÉ¬≤ perms, 3 with T‚ÇÇ¬≤¬∑T‚ÇÉ perms) to give a pure
ring identity in `(z, P, T‚ÇÇ, T‚ÇÉ, T‚ÇÑ, T‚ÇÖ)` where each RHS term is deg-8+.

Pairings (additions on top of septic):
- 3 weight-1 terms `z^i¬∑(P-T‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÑ)¬∑z^j` extend to `z^i¬∑(P-T‚ÇÇ-T‚ÇÉ-T‚ÇÑ-T‚ÇÖ)¬∑z^j`.
- `z¬∑T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÑ` and `z¬∑T‚ÇÑ¬∑T‚ÇÇ` + `z¬∑T‚ÇÉ¬≤` get absorbed into
  `z¬∑(P¬≤ - T‚ÇÇ¬≤ - T‚ÇÇT‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉT‚ÇÇ)` ‚Üí `z¬∑(P¬≤ - T‚ÇÇ¬≤ - T‚ÇÇT‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉT‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÇT‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÉ¬≤ - T‚ÇÑT‚ÇÇ)`.
- Conjugates `(...)¬∑z` and `T_aux¬∑z¬∑T_aux` get the analogous extensions.
- `T‚ÇÇ¬≤¬∑T‚ÇÉ`, `T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÉ¬∑T‚ÇÇ`, `T‚ÇÉ¬∑T‚ÇÇ¬≤` get absorbed into `P¬≥`:
  `(P¬≥ - T‚ÇÇ¬≥)` ‚Üí `(P¬≥ - T‚ÇÇ¬≥ - T‚ÇÇ¬≤¬∑T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÇ¬∑T‚ÇÉ¬∑T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ¬∑T‚ÇÇ¬≤)`.

Each RHS summand is deg-8+ in the BCH context.
Proof: `noncomm_ring` (pure ring identity, no scalar coefficients). -/
private theorem I2_octic_residual_decomp_eq (z P T‚ÇÇ T‚ÇÉ T‚ÇÑ T‚ÇÖ : ùî∏) :
    (z + P) ^ 3 - z ^ 3 -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÇ + z * T‚ÇÇ * z + T‚ÇÇ * z ^ 2) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÉ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 + T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ + T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 * z) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÑ + z * T‚ÇÑ * z + T‚ÇÑ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÉ + T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ * z +
        T‚ÇÇ ^ 3) -
      (z ^ 2 * T‚ÇÖ + z * T‚ÇÖ * z + T‚ÇÖ * z ^ 2 +
        z * T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÑ + z * T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÉ + z * T‚ÇÑ * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÑ + T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÉ + T‚ÇÑ * z * T‚ÇÇ +
        T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÑ * z + T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÉ * z + T‚ÇÑ * T‚ÇÇ * z +
        T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ + T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ + T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÇ) =
    z ^ 2 * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÖ) + z * (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÖ) * z +
      (P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÖ) * z ^ 2 +
    z * (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ -
         T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ * T‚ÇÇ) +
    (P * z * P - T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÇ -
         T‚ÇÇ * z * T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÉ * z * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ * z * T‚ÇÇ) +
    (P ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 - T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ -
         T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÑ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ * T‚ÇÇ) * z +
    (P ^ 3 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 3 - T‚ÇÇ ^ 2 * T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÇ * T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ * T‚ÇÇ ^ 2) := by
  noncomm_ring

