/-- **I‚ÇÅ octic residual decomposition** (pure algebraic identity in (ea, eb, a, b)):
extends `I1_septic_residual_decomp_eq` by additionally subtracting
`corr‚ÇÅ_7 = ¬Ω¬∑W7`, expressing
`(I‚ÇÅ in quartic_id form) - corr‚ÇÅ - corr‚ÇÅ_5 - corr‚ÇÅ_6 - corr‚ÇÅ_7`
as 13 deg-8+ terms (a one-degree-higher promotion of the septic RHS).

