/-- Norm bound `‚Äñy¬≥ - z¬≥ - y3_4‚Äñ ‚â§ 19¬∑s‚Åµ` where `z = y - P`,
`y3_4 = z¬≤¬∑T‚ÇÇ + z¬∑T‚ÇÇ¬∑z + T‚ÇÇ¬∑z¬≤`, for `s ‚â§ 1`. Used in the y5 octic
