/-- **P ‚àí T‚ÇÇ ‚àí T‚ÇÉ ‚àí T‚ÇÑ algebraic decomposition**: pure ring identity in
`(ea, eb, a, b)` expressing `P - T‚ÇÇ - T‚ÇÉ - T‚ÇÑ` as a sum of 7 deg-5+ terms.
Used in `norm_P_sub_T2_sub_T3_sub_T4_le`.

